WEBVTT

00:01.927 --> 00:03.505
I remember raising my hand up

00:03.507 --> 00:04.772
and pulling back the curtains,

00:04.927 --> 00:07.045
and that's when I came
face-to-face

00:07.121 --> 00:09.652
with what we now know
as a Grey.

00:09.807 --> 00:12.152
Millions of people claiming

00:12.307 --> 00:16.485
to be abducted
by extraterrestrials.

00:16.541 --> 00:19.279
How many of you have had
an experience

00:19.281 --> 00:21.619
- of having been abducted?
- Wow.

00:21.794 --> 00:26.252
Ancient stories
of humans brought off planet

00:26.407 --> 00:28.399
by otherworldly beings.

00:28.421 --> 00:32.552
Angels, demons, spirits...

00:32.641 --> 00:35.565
are these the same
extraterrestrial entities

00:35.567 --> 00:39.079
who are interacting
with us today?

00:39.101 --> 00:44.039
My mother and I both had this
dreamlike experience

00:44.061 --> 00:45.739
of being taken to a craft.

00:45.894 --> 00:49.912
And I saw these
nonhuman entities.

00:49.914 --> 00:53.812
Could these incredible
stories really be true?

00:53.921 --> 00:58.185
And if so, why are humans
being taken?

00:58.241 --> 01:00.159
You have to ask yourself

01:00.334 --> 01:02.752
what is really going on here?
Because these cases

01:02.841 --> 01:05.364
simply defy explanation.

