a three-day event to discuss
and explore the possibility

01:57.514 --> 02:01.259
that intelligent life exists
beyond our planet,

02:01.261 --> 02:04.792
and may have visited Earth
in the distant past.

02:04.794 --> 02:08.192
It's one thing for people to say

02:08.366 --> 02:11.285
that not only have they
seen a UFO,

02:11.287 --> 02:14.225
but they've had an experience,
a contact...

02:14.281 --> 02:15.612
During one panel
led by former

02:15.767 --> 02:18.845
Ministry of Defence
investigator Nick Pope,

02:18.847 --> 02:21.585
a group of experts talk about
a significant

02:21.587 --> 02:24.359
and controversial subject:

02:24.381 --> 02:26.885
alien abductions.

02:26.887 --> 02:28.959
Looking out at all of you,

02:29.134 --> 02:32.545
one of the things that we would
like to know is,

02:32.547 --> 02:37.012
how many of you have had
an experience you think

02:37.187 --> 02:39.239
might involve
having been abducted?

02:39.261 --> 02:43.779
Can you all put your hands up
who think that you have been?

02:45.361 --> 02:48.545
Wow, that's a lot of people.

02:48.601 --> 02:51.019
If anyone feels comfortable

02:51.194 --> 02:53.312
about coming up
to the microphone,

02:53.467 --> 02:56.985
we would love to hear
your stories.

02:57.161 --> 02:59.305
So, uh, please, yeah.

02:59.307 --> 03:00.479
My name's, uh, Alice Green.

03:00.634 --> 03:03.619
And, um, 40 years ago,

03:03.774 --> 03:08.219
uh, when I was 15, I, um,
I had an abduction experience.

03:08.261 --> 03:11.165
There was a huge spaceship
over my house,

03:11.167 --> 03:13.117
and, uh, one minute I'm in my
bed and the next minute

03:13.141 --> 03:14.932
I'm up in the spaceship.

03:15.087 --> 03:17.872
I wanted to call it a dream,

03:17.874 --> 03:19.772
because I didn't want to call it
an abduction experience

03:19.774 --> 03:22.219
for a long time.

03:22.221 --> 03:23.861
I started having
one of those experiences,

03:23.901 --> 03:29.859
out of body, but not just in
the vicinity.

03:29.861 --> 03:32.239
I kind of started entering
the space realm,

03:32.394 --> 03:34.812
and I just kept going.

03:34.967 --> 03:37.399
And it just got scarier
and scarier for me.

03:37.401 --> 03:39.339
I didn't know what was going on.

03:39.494 --> 03:40.919
The alien that I spoke to

03:41.074 --> 03:42.985
was about to my shoulder,

03:43.041 --> 03:44.645
maybe four and a half feet tall,

03:44.701 --> 03:46.352
and he had three fingers.

03:46.354 --> 03:49.819
He was like
your typical grey alien.

03:49.821 --> 03:51.310
And I had several encounters
over the course

03:51.334 --> 03:53.332
of the next couple years.

03:53.334 --> 03:55.319
I never wanted to tell anybody
because I thought my friends

03:55.341 --> 03:57.326
and family would think
I was crazy.

03:57.328 --> 03:58.739
Millions of people

03:58.894 --> 04:02.265
taken by
extraterrestrial beings?

04:02.267 --> 04:05.419
If alien abductions
are happening,

04:05.574 --> 04:08.339
as experiencers at this panel

04:08.341 --> 04:11.179
and many other
alleged abductees claim,

04:11.181 --> 04:14.499
what evidence is there
to support their stories?

04:14.521 --> 04:19.379
As the number of recorded
abduction cases has increased

04:19.401 --> 04:23.152
over the last several decades,
experts in a variety of fields

04:23.307 --> 04:26.819
have worked
to find this evidence.

04:26.821 --> 04:30.685
In 1991, my colleague
Budd Hopkins and I

04:30.687 --> 04:34.599
got funding for a national poll
about the abduction phenomenon

04:34.774 --> 04:36.985
through the Roper Organization.

04:37.161 --> 04:40.972
We found that at least two
percent of the American public,

04:41.127 --> 04:44.245
and at most, perhaps even five
percent of the American public,

04:44.401 --> 04:46.219
were abductees.

04:46.394 --> 04:50.252
Even with two percent, we're
dealing with an enormous number

04:50.254 --> 04:52.932
of people who've been abducted
throughout the world.

04:53.087 --> 04:55.319
Of course, when people
from the outside

04:55.474 --> 04:57.085
look at
the abduction phenomenon,

04:57.261 --> 05:00.099
they think that
this is just neurological.

05:00.121 --> 05:01.965
I wish that was the case.

05:02.141 --> 05:06.232
That would be wonderful
if that were the case.

05:06.407 --> 05:09.052
I can say, from having
interviewed now

05:09.207 --> 05:12.779
about 1,600 people
in the abduction syndrome,

05:12.801 --> 05:15.519
there are common denominators.

05:15.541 --> 05:20.739
I would say the vast majority
don't know details.

05:20.761 --> 05:24.625
They just remember pieces.

05:24.681 --> 05:27.999
They might remember,
"I saw these eyes,

05:28.021 --> 05:31.219
and they were big and black
and slanted."

05:31.374 --> 05:34.372
They will hear either
a buzzing sound,

05:34.527 --> 05:37.459
or there might be a clicking.

05:37.481 --> 05:41.105
Or in the room, there might be,
like, a little orb of light,

05:41.161 --> 05:43.265
or several orbs of light.

05:43.321 --> 05:46.419
They won't be able to move.

05:46.421 --> 05:50.485
And the paralysis is always
described the same way.

05:50.641 --> 05:54.785
They can move their eyes,
they can see.

05:54.841 --> 05:58.139
They can't move their head.

05:58.294 --> 06:02.979
They will say they see their
bedroom wall just disappear.

06:03.134 --> 06:06.105
Or they are taken
right through the wall.

06:06.261 --> 06:08.899
Or they're taken
through a window.

06:09.054 --> 06:12.245
Or they are taken
through the ceiling.

06:12.421 --> 06:16.305
And then 100% of people,

06:16.461 --> 06:21.645
their next consciousness is
waking up, often the sun is up,

06:21.801 --> 06:24.145
and they know
something's happened,

06:24.201 --> 06:26.352
but they don't know what.

06:26.461 --> 06:29.372
Well,
when you start adding it up

06:29.381 --> 06:31.252
across 40, 50,000 cases,

06:31.254 --> 06:33.145
the number one piece
of compelling evidence

06:33.301 --> 06:36.119
is the credibility
of the individual.

06:36.294 --> 06:39.405
We have doctors,
lawyers, politicians.

06:39.561 --> 06:42.432
So these are people
who have a lot at stake

06:42.434 --> 06:44.239
if they were to say,
"Hey, I've been abducted

06:44.394 --> 06:45.834
by an alien,"
or something like this,

06:45.927 --> 06:50.212
so you have to take
those people seriously.

06:50.367 --> 06:53.379
There are really only two
possibilities here.

06:53.381 --> 06:56.092
Either we're dealing
with a mass delusion

06:56.267 --> 06:59.519
on an unprecedented scale,

06:59.694 --> 07:05.119
or what these people are saying
is actually literally happening

07:05.274 --> 07:10.039
in a physical sense, and these
alien abductions are real.

07:13.207 --> 07:15.759
But if millions
of people have been abducted

07:15.914 --> 07:19.679
by extraterrestrials... or even
a fraction of that number...

07:19.834 --> 07:22.792
what could be
the reason behind it?

07:22.947 --> 07:24.492
And why now?

07:24.667 --> 07:28.119
While what we call
alien abductions

07:28.274 --> 07:31.285
may only have been reported
in modern times,

07:31.361 --> 07:34.532
ancient astronaut theorists
claim there is evidence

07:34.534 --> 07:36.632
that this phenomenon
has been happening

07:36.741 --> 07:39.265
for thousands of years.

07:39.441 --> 07:41.992
In ancient biblical texts,

07:41.994 --> 07:46.745
and also in other textual
references, we have accounts

07:46.747 --> 07:52.165
of people ascending and
descending from and to the sky

07:52.167 --> 07:57.659
with fiery chariots
and flying type of craft.

07:57.834 --> 08:02.085
And that to me indicates that
what these accounts refer to

08:02.087 --> 08:06.925
are similar
to modern-day abductions.

08:06.927 --> 08:09.865
Those accounts
are eyewitness accounts.

08:09.941 --> 08:13.099
They're not told
in the third person,

08:13.101 --> 08:15.545
but it's actually
"I, Ezekiel, witnessed."

08:15.701 --> 08:17.545
"I, Enoch, witnessed."

08:17.601 --> 08:19.185
"I, Abraham, did this."

08:19.187 --> 08:20.945
"I walked through there."

08:20.947 --> 08:26.072
Also, in ancient China,
and also, in ancient Egypt,

08:26.247 --> 08:29.319
are there stories of people
having been visited

08:29.494 --> 08:34.879
or having gone up to the sky to
visit with the so-called gods.

08:35.034 --> 08:40.924
What better way to describe
an extraterrestrial encounter?

08:41.081 --> 08:44.905
So today, we call it
an "alien abduction."

08:44.961 --> 08:50.765
In previous centuries, it was
called by different names.

08:50.921 --> 08:53.085
But we recognize
from the experience

08:53.241 --> 08:54.852
that they are identical.

08:55.027 --> 08:58.179
And therefore, it adds validity

08:58.354 --> 09:04.092
to this not being a modern myth,
but a very ancient problem.

09:04.201 --> 09:08.332
Why today, then,
is it such an important issue?

09:08.487 --> 09:11.172
It very well may be that we did
not recognize in the past

09:11.174 --> 09:13.665
how widespread
these experiences were.

09:13.667 --> 09:18.099
Or it could be that there
is a stepping up of the agenda,

09:18.254 --> 09:20.972
and that the experience
is spreading greater,

09:20.974 --> 09:23.339
farther and wider
than it was in the past.

09:25.434 --> 09:27.345
Could these
extraordinary accounts,

09:27.347 --> 09:31.812
both past and present, be
describing an ongoing program

09:31.967 --> 09:35.479
of human abduction,
in spite of the skepticism

09:35.634 --> 09:37.679
with which they are
viewed by the public?

09:39.714 --> 09:43.892
And is there a smoking gun
that will finally establish

09:44.047 --> 09:48.232
that this phenomenon is real,
and still underway?

09:48.387 --> 09:52.492
Perhaps further clues
can be found by examining

09:52.501 --> 09:55.859
one of the most well-documented
cases on record.

10:02.014 --> 10:04.979
Sheffield, Massachusetts.

10:05.001 --> 10:08.732
June 11, 2018.

10:08.734 --> 10:11.059
Well, we're pretty much
here now.

10:11.214 --> 10:14.299
Author and researcher Mike Bara

10:14.301 --> 10:17.939
has joined abduction experiencer
Thom Reed to visit the site

10:18.094 --> 10:22.825
where Thom says he and members
of his family were abducted

10:22.827 --> 10:27.485
after encountering a strange UFO
nearly 50 years ago.

10:27.487 --> 10:31.279
Does it evoke any memories or
emotions, bring back anything?

10:31.434 --> 10:32.479
Like an anxiety.

10:32.654 --> 10:34.632
- Really?
- Or nervousness I guess.

10:34.787 --> 10:37.445
The UFO was reportedly seen,

10:37.621 --> 10:39.959
not only by the Reed family,

10:40.114 --> 10:42.119
but also by multiple witnesses

10:42.121 --> 10:44.532
all across
Western Massachusetts.

10:44.687 --> 10:46.705
Okay. So, I guess here we are.

10:46.707 --> 10:49.212
- This is the spot, right?
- This is it.

10:49.367 --> 10:51.585
Can you kind of paint me
a picture of what was going on

10:51.761 --> 10:52.779
that night,
what happened the day

10:52.801 --> 10:54.219
- you drove up this road?
- Sure.

10:54.374 --> 10:55.957
Well, first of all,
it was, like, 90 degrees.

10:55.981 --> 10:57.450
It was a really hot night,
and there were

10:57.474 --> 10:58.754
an awful lot of families outside

10:58.801 --> 11:00.619
because it was Labor Day.

11:00.774 --> 11:03.679
It was September 1, 1969,
which was a Labor Day holiday.

11:03.681 --> 11:06.079
Okay. Can you describe what
people saw? I mean, did they see

11:06.081 --> 11:07.877
- just a light in the sky?
- They all saw something

11:07.901 --> 11:09.432
- a little bit different.
- What do you remember

11:09.434 --> 11:10.903
about what happened to you
and your family?

11:10.927 --> 11:12.439
There's a lot of time
that went by,

11:12.614 --> 11:14.392
and I only remember
little pieces of it.

11:14.394 --> 11:17.245
But, uh, we were coming
right down this road here,

11:17.247 --> 11:19.539
and we were heading
through the bridge.

11:19.694 --> 11:21.792
- Mm-hmm.
- And, uh, let-let me show you.

11:21.794 --> 11:23.865
- Okay. Sure.
- All right?

11:24.021 --> 11:27.419
At 9:00 p.m.
on the night of the sighting,

11:27.574 --> 11:30.599
ten-year-old Thom
and his mother, grandmother

11:30.641 --> 11:33.272
and brother were just minutes

11:33.274 --> 11:37.245
from getting home
when they crossed the bridge.

11:37.401 --> 11:39.650
Well, I was in the back seat
behind the driver, my mother.

11:39.674 --> 11:41.232
- Mm-hmm.
- And my grandmother,

11:41.387 --> 11:42.777
who was sitting
in the passenger seat,

11:42.801 --> 11:44.705
was the first one to notice
that there was a...

11:44.707 --> 11:46.699
an odd light
that didn't seem to make sense.

11:46.741 --> 11:50.132
There was a bleed of light
coming through the bridge.

11:50.307 --> 11:53.385
So light was coming
through places

11:53.387 --> 11:54.790
it should not have been
if it was just headlights.

11:54.814 --> 11:56.283
Yeah, it was coming
through the walls a little bit,

11:56.307 --> 11:58.319
coming through the floorboards.

11:58.494 --> 11:59.745
Then we exited the bridge.

11:59.901 --> 12:02.939
This is the spot right there.

12:03.114 --> 12:04.477
This is where
we first saw it, Mike.

12:04.501 --> 12:06.025
So, um,

12:06.181 --> 12:08.065
- can you describe what you saw?
- Yeah.

12:08.067 --> 12:10.665
It was like an orb,
if you would, or a sphere,

12:10.821 --> 12:14.379
and it was about, I'm gonna say
maybe 30, 40 yards round.

12:14.534 --> 12:16.692
It was a perfectly round sphere,

12:16.694 --> 12:19.765
and it had rods of light
that seemed to fire from it.

12:19.921 --> 12:23.445
So it looked like a shiver cone,
or an ice cream cone.

12:23.447 --> 12:26.692
So, none of you has ever seen
anything like this before?

12:26.694 --> 12:28.699
No, not like that, no.

12:28.741 --> 12:30.692
As Thom's mother continued

12:30.701 --> 12:32.692
driving slowly down the road,

12:32.847 --> 12:35.719
the object flew on a route
parallel to theirs

12:35.721 --> 12:40.339
until it took an abrupt turn,
cutting them off.

12:40.361 --> 12:42.699
The car comes to a stop,

12:42.701 --> 12:45.219
and there's a feeling
that came over the car,

12:45.374 --> 12:46.992
which was like a...
some type of a field.

12:47.147 --> 12:50.219
And we were just gone.
We aren't in the car anymore.

12:55.101 --> 12:58.905
And I remember seeing a light
or a door of some kind.

12:59.061 --> 13:01.092
And I was grabbed like this
on my left arm.

13:01.247 --> 13:03.892
And I was kind of pushed
towards this door.

13:04.067 --> 13:06.319
I went into the door.

13:06.494 --> 13:09.892
And I was sitting on...
almost like a-an autopsy table.

13:10.047 --> 13:12.805
And I saw what looked like

13:12.807 --> 13:16.079
some type of a large insect,
like an ant, if you will.

13:16.254 --> 13:19.072
Very stick-like legs,
bamboo almost.

13:19.227 --> 13:23.132
And that's what frightened me,
and then I was out.

13:23.134 --> 13:25.199
Then I remember waking
in the back of the car.

13:27.147 --> 13:31.845
If you could... remember

13:31.847 --> 13:34.499
every single detail,
every single thing that happened

13:34.654 --> 13:37.772
- to you, would you want to?
- I want to know,

13:37.774 --> 13:40.652
but at the same time,
I'm not sure I...

13:40.654 --> 13:42.865
that's a good thing
at this point.

13:43.021 --> 13:44.892
It's-it's confusing.

13:44.901 --> 13:48.125
You know, I kind of need to know
everything that happened,

13:48.127 --> 13:50.567
but at the same time, there's
really no way for me to do that.

13:52.781 --> 13:55.499
For years following
the reported event,

13:55.654 --> 13:57.859
a number of local authorities
and UFO investigators

13:58.014 --> 13:59.685
tried to find evidence

13:59.741 --> 14:04.379
that would validate the Reed
family's incredible account.

14:04.534 --> 14:08.245
One of these was a local judge
named Kevin Titus,

14:08.401 --> 14:11.905
who has spent decades
interviewing eyewitnesses

14:12.061 --> 14:14.685
and verifying their testimony.

14:14.861 --> 14:18.605
It is his belief that enough
evidence exists to conclude

14:18.681 --> 14:21.839
that something otherworldly did,
in fact,

14:21.841 --> 14:26.805
happen on that summer night
nearly 50 years ago.

14:26.807 --> 14:28.697
Everybody couldn't explain
what they were seeing.

14:28.721 --> 14:30.652
People were saying...
calling in WSBS radio,

14:30.807 --> 14:32.319
and telling them

14:32.474 --> 14:34.639
that there's something going on
over in this area.

14:34.814 --> 14:37.892
And, uh, nobody was able to

14:37.894 --> 14:41.419
completely say what it was,
but everybody saw it.

14:41.441 --> 14:43.959
There was well over 250 people
that called in.

14:44.134 --> 14:46.799
They were scared, hysterical.

14:46.954 --> 14:49.185
Some people couldn't explain
what they saw.

14:49.187 --> 14:51.279
They called the police.

14:51.434 --> 14:53.299
And they called
the Army Reserve Air Base.

14:53.341 --> 14:55.319
It's a fact, it did happen.

14:55.341 --> 14:58.179
When you have over 250 people
that saw something the same day,

14:58.221 --> 14:59.639
how can you say it wasn't true?

15:02.001 --> 15:04.792
Over 250 callers?

15:04.947 --> 15:10.779
And all reportedly seeing the
same unidentified flying object?

15:10.801 --> 15:14.092
For abduction researchers
and local authorities,

15:14.094 --> 15:16.792
the incredible number
of witnesses

15:16.794 --> 15:18.079
gave the Reed family's case

15:18.101 --> 15:21.879
an uncommonly high level
of credibility.

15:21.901 --> 15:27.092
So much so
that on November 3, 2015,

15:27.094 --> 15:31.605
Massachusetts Governor Charles
D. Baker issued a citation

15:31.761 --> 15:33.192
which formally recognized

15:33.367 --> 15:36.639
that a verified UFO event
had taken place,

15:36.661 --> 15:41.905
just as the Reed family
and many others had described.

15:42.061 --> 15:45.552
To date, no other
alien encounter has received

15:45.727 --> 15:49.405
this kind of acknowledgement.

15:49.481 --> 15:52.579
What I think is important
in all this is

15:52.601 --> 15:56.912
that we were the first to be
state-inducted as a true event.

15:56.914 --> 16:00.039
And I think that opens doors,
and paves the way for a lot

16:00.194 --> 16:02.479
of other people who deserve
to be taken more seriously.

16:04.007 --> 16:05.892
Do the verified accounts

16:05.981 --> 16:08.699
of the Sheffield incident
refute skeptics

16:08.854 --> 16:12.279
who claim that abduction stories
are unreliable?

16:12.454 --> 16:16.945
Ancient astronaut theorists
say yes, and they suggest

16:17.101 --> 16:19.785
that even more compelling
evidence can be found

16:19.787 --> 16:25.459
by examining memories buried
deep inside... the human mind.

16:30.221 --> 16:32.559
At one of the AlienCon panels

16:32.714 --> 16:35.692
examining
alien abduction phenomena,

16:35.847 --> 16:38.565
a member of the audience shares
what he believes

16:38.567 --> 16:41.585
to have been
a real-life alien encounter,

16:41.661 --> 16:43.699
one involving missing time.

16:43.854 --> 16:46.085
In about 1996,

16:46.161 --> 16:50.212
I saw a UFO, and it scared me
