a story that actually
began three years prior

33:13.401 --> 33:16.985
with an incident
involving Betty's sister.

33:16.987 --> 33:21.532
Betty Hill was my aunt,
my mother's sister.

33:21.534 --> 33:25.825
Something that we have
never revealed before

33:25.827 --> 33:30.505
is that my mother had
a close encounter in 1958.

33:30.581 --> 33:34.452
She saw this huge,
cigar-shaped craft

33:34.627 --> 33:36.972
hovering over a field.

33:37.127 --> 33:42.485
She had no explanation for what
had happened as far as she knew.

33:42.641 --> 33:46.172
She had gone shopping
and she had driven home.

33:46.327 --> 33:50.685
My mother eventually
underwent hypnosis

33:50.687 --> 33:54.225
and through hypnosis,
she recalled

33:54.381 --> 33:57.019
having been abducted as well.

33:57.174 --> 34:01.392
And I also had this uncanny

34:01.481 --> 34:03.492
sort of dreamlike experience

34:03.494 --> 34:06.312
of being taken to a craft.

34:06.467 --> 34:10.018
It bothered me
for many, many years.

34:10.174 --> 34:14.331
Eventually, I did talk
to my family about it

34:14.333 --> 34:18.379
and that's when I found out that
my mother had the same memory.

34:18.420 --> 34:21.458
Could it be
that extraterrestrial beings

34:21.614 --> 34:24.572
are abducting
not only individuals,

34:24.681 --> 34:26.438
but also families?

34:26.460 --> 34:29.752
And if so, why?

34:29.754 --> 34:32.445
The abduction phenomenon
is intergenerational.

34:32.621 --> 34:34.712
When a man and a woman marry

34:34.867 --> 34:37.559
and either the man
or the woman is an abductee,

34:37.714 --> 34:40.225
their children
will be abductees.

34:40.226 --> 34:45.445
It seems that specific
bloodlines are involved here.

34:45.601 --> 34:47.784
And if that's the case,

34:47.786 --> 34:50.612
it raises
the intriguing possibility

34:50.766 --> 34:54.772
that the extraterrestrials are
interested in human biology,

34:54.927 --> 34:57.799
that they are monitoring
specific genetic lines

34:57.821 --> 34:59.739
for some purpose.

34:59.914 --> 35:04.445
For ancient astronaut
theorists and UFO researchers,

35:04.601 --> 35:07.105
the notion that
extraterrestrials

35:07.181 --> 35:09.992
are conducting experiments
involving human biology

35:10.101 --> 35:11.659
is not a new one.

35:11.814 --> 35:14.705
Many believe the practice
has been going on

35:14.861 --> 35:18.759
for thousands of years.

35:18.914 --> 35:21.272
Maybe there's some truth
to these entities

35:21.427 --> 35:23.419
which we call <i> shedim.</i>

35:23.574 --> 35:25.312
These are old legends

35:25.467 --> 35:29.812
of people who are abducted,
sexually seduced

35:29.967 --> 35:33.279
and some taken away.

35:33.434 --> 35:36.145
And when we hear today
about the numerous stories

35:36.301 --> 35:39.619
of alien abductions
throughout history,

35:39.621 --> 35:41.952
they are identical.

35:42.107 --> 35:44.119
For proof that their theories

35:44.274 --> 35:48.025
about the biological nature
of alien abductions are valid,

35:48.081 --> 35:50.125
researchers point to the fact

35:50.127 --> 35:54.479
that a relatively high number
of abductees, more than 60%,

35:54.521 --> 35:57.545
have an extraordinarily
rare blood type:

35:57.601 --> 36:00.559
Rh negative.

36:00.714 --> 36:05.805
The subject kept coming up from
the abductees: "I'm Rh negative."

36:05.807 --> 36:09.419
"Could it have anything to do
with why I'm being abducted?"

36:09.441 --> 36:15.039
I got to collaborate with a
doctor, Dr. John Altshuler,

36:15.214 --> 36:19.225
and he did pathology;
he did blood work.

36:19.281 --> 36:24.605
And he gave the conclusion
that Rh negative blood

36:24.761 --> 36:29.645
might actually be
a genetic data point

36:29.721 --> 36:35.539
about why humans
could be hybrids,

36:35.541 --> 36:38.405
that every Rh negative

36:38.581 --> 36:41.932
would be coming
from a history of abductions.

36:42.107 --> 36:45.985
Rh negative
is a very peculiar thing.

36:45.987 --> 36:49.172
First off, it didn't exist
until 35,000 years ago.

36:49.347 --> 36:52.159
It may have been
that 35,000 years ago,

36:52.201 --> 36:54.259
E.T. introduced this
into our society

36:54.414 --> 36:57.319
through whatever breeding
programs they've been running.

36:57.321 --> 37:00.199
The ancient astronaut
theory suggests

37:00.354 --> 37:03.199
that for thousands of years,

37:03.201 --> 37:05.879
extraterrestrials
meddled with our DNA.

37:05.921 --> 37:10.685
There was a time when
we were <i> Homo sapiens.</i>

37:10.861 --> 37:14.205
And then we became
<i>Homo sapiens sapiens.</i>

37:14.361 --> 37:17.659
And that happened
within only 50,000 years,

37:17.814 --> 37:20.719
which by Darwinian
evolutionary standards,

37:20.874 --> 37:24.745
is too short of a time span
for that to happen.

37:24.901 --> 37:29.672
Our brain volume increased
by up to 30%

37:29.847 --> 37:32.939
in 50,000 years,
which is absolutely crazy.

37:33.094 --> 37:35.972
Now, the reason why I think

37:36.127 --> 37:39.232
that modern-day abductions occur

37:39.321 --> 37:44.659
is because maybe we are still
being manipulated with our DNA

37:44.661 --> 37:46.692
from extraterrestrials

37:46.781 --> 37:50.185
in order to turn us
from <i> Homo sapiens sapiens</i>

37:50.261 --> 37:54.139
into <i> Homo sapiens</i>
<i>sapiens sapiens.</i>

37:54.181 --> 37:57.919
Have extraterrestrials
been abducting people

37:58.094 --> 38:01.752
in order to monitor the
evolutionary progress of humans?

38:01.841 --> 38:06.099
Or have they been deliberately
manipulating our biology

38:06.254 --> 38:09.012
in order to achieve
some ultimate purpose?

38:09.167 --> 38:12.305
Ancient astronaut
theorists claim

38:12.307 --> 38:16.405
that both possibilities are
likely true and for this reason,

38:16.561 --> 38:20.605
it is more important than ever
for us to hear the stories

38:20.661 --> 38:24.159
of those who say
they have been taken.

38:29.894 --> 38:31.759
Pasadena, California.

38:31.914 --> 38:36.252
June 16, 2018.

38:36.261 --> 38:40.165
Throughout a discussion
about alien abductions

38:40.321 --> 38:42.079
during a panel at AlienCon,

38:42.254 --> 38:45.885
both the panelists
and members of the audience

38:45.887 --> 38:48.592
remark on how difficult,
but also important it is

38:48.747 --> 38:51.972
to speak out about abductions.

38:52.127 --> 38:55.239
I hesitated coming up here
for a couple reasons.

38:55.414 --> 38:58.812
Um...

38:58.967 --> 39:02.899
Every topic
that you guys have mentioned

39:03.074 --> 39:06.239
has connected dots
actively right now today.

39:06.394 --> 39:09.359
As far as lineage,
as far as bloodlines,

39:09.361 --> 39:11.105
as far as families,
so generational.

39:11.161 --> 39:14.645
My mom, um, myself, my daughter.

39:14.647 --> 39:16.185
I had night terrors as a child,

39:16.361 --> 39:18.532
missing time as a child
throughout my life.

39:18.534 --> 39:21.205
I literally have
short-term memory deficits

39:21.261 --> 39:25.059
and specific things,
real spontaneous phenomenon

39:25.214 --> 39:27.705
that ultimately touches
on everything that

39:27.861 --> 39:29.901
- you guys are talking about.
- Thank you very much.

39:30.014 --> 39:32.679
These hardly ever seem
to be one-off experiences.

39:32.854 --> 39:34.319
Thank you
for sharing your story.

39:37.354 --> 39:39.939
I'd like to say, uh, I applaud
you guys for your courage

39:40.094 --> 39:41.490
to come forward in front
of all these people

39:41.514 --> 39:42.779
and share your story.

39:42.934 --> 39:45.112
I'm blown away
by the amount of people

39:45.267 --> 39:47.072
that, uh, show up at this panel.

39:47.227 --> 39:50.025
And when I see this kind of, uh,
support, it's very encouraging

39:50.181 --> 39:51.532
and I think
that's very important

39:51.687 --> 39:53.932
to bring this phenomenon
out into the light

39:53.934 --> 39:55.865
where it needs to be
because a lot of answers

39:55.867 --> 39:57.645
lie with the experiencers.

39:57.821 --> 39:59.079
So I just thank you for that.

40:04.681 --> 40:08.165
Coming forward to admit
that you've had some type

40:08.321 --> 40:11.892
of a close encounter,
whether it is seeing something

40:11.901 --> 40:14.112
or maybe you've been abducted,

40:14.267 --> 40:17.039
that is a very difficult
thing to admit.

40:17.194 --> 40:20.599
And that is why I think

40:20.774 --> 40:24.285
we really should look at all
the other pieces of evidence:

40:24.287 --> 40:27.699
abduction cases
or close encounters

40:27.854 --> 40:30.392
and say, "Okay, what if?"

40:30.394 --> 40:34.372
I'm happy today that
I'm finally able to say

40:34.527 --> 40:37.699
it's not only real,
it's happening.

40:37.701 --> 40:41.065
Great. Hearing those stories
is of help

40:41.067 --> 40:44.765
to any of you out there who have
had these strange experiences.

40:44.921 --> 40:47.119
And you are not alone with this,
as you can see.

40:47.121 --> 40:50.639
So thank you to you and thank
you to my fellow panelists.

40:50.794 --> 40:55.139
When you look
at the vast body of data

40:55.294 --> 40:57.785
that we have on this phenomenon,

40:57.961 --> 40:59.732
it's difficult
to avoid the conclusion

40:59.907 --> 41:01.725
that something is going on here.

41:01.781 --> 41:03.799
Why should we, therefore,

41:03.954 --> 41:06.959
cast away the stories
of the abductees

41:06.981 --> 41:09.619
just because we may feel
a little uncomfortable

41:09.774 --> 41:11.539
with the place that takes us?

41:13.701 --> 41:15.992
Each year, thousands of people

41:16.147 --> 41:18.225
are bravely coming forward

41:18.301 --> 41:21.645
with personal accounts
of alien abductions.

41:21.821 --> 41:24.372
But is the world's
growing willingness

41:24.527 --> 41:27.352
to hear them and
believe them a sign

41:27.354 --> 41:29.559
that humanity
might be on the brink

41:29.714 --> 41:33.439
of an exciting new period
in its evolution,

41:33.481 --> 41:38.352
one where we will discover
that centuries of alien contact

41:38.361 --> 41:40.919
has changed us in ways
we could never

41:40.941 --> 41:43.545
have previously imagined
or accepted?

41:43.601 --> 41:47.332
Perhaps a greater acceptance

41:47.487 --> 41:49.645
that alien contact is being made

41:49.801 --> 41:52.259
will prepare us for the future,

41:52.281 --> 41:56.019
a future where we will become

41:56.041 --> 41:59.559
the extraterrestrials
on other worlds

41:59.714 --> 42:04.879
and encounter other life-forms
not so different from our own.

